# Never commit ML artifacts — they are exactly what we audit
*.pkl
*.h5
*.keras
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.safetensors
# Exception: explicit test fixtures live under tests/fixtures/ — those are intentional
!tests/fixtures/**/*.pkl
!tests/fixtures/**/*.h5
!tests/fixtures/**/*.keras

# Claude workspace — personal overrides + per-developer memory
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/memory/
!.claude/memory/README.md
